NovaArch Live Environment
-------------------------
Light KDE Plasma desktop on Arch — windows, panels, and System Settings work like a typical PC.

Live logs in as user live (no password). Connect Wi‑Fi from the network icon, then Welcome → Launch Installer (archinstall).

Displays: System Settings → Display. Application launcher: Meta (Windows) key.

Useful commands:
  novaarch-launch-installer   (or: sudo archinstall)
  nmtui
  systemsettings
